## **🔐 SECURITY & RISK PROTECTION**

### **Built-in Safety Features:**

```
1. Daily Loss Limit
   If you lose $50 in one day → Bot stops trading

2. Max Consecutive Losses
   If you lose 3 trades in a row → Bot pauses

3. Minimum Confidence
   Bot only trades signals above 75% confidence

4. Position Sizing
   Bot never risks more than 5% per trade

5. Daily Trade Limit
   Bot stops after 20 trades per day

6. Cooling Period
   After a loss, bot waits 15 minutes before next trade

7. Balance Check
   Bot checks your IQ Option balance before each trade
```

